<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 02 at 1:18AM EST  by NWS Detroit</headline>
<description>...LIGHT SNOW CONTINUES THROUGH THE MID MORNING HOURS...
Widespread light snow will continue through the mid-morning hours
with temperatures now in the mid 20s. Fluctuations in snowfall
intensity and reductions in visibility is expected with the
ongoing activity. Drivers are urged to exercise caution and take
it slow through the overnight hours.
&amp;&amp;
PRECAUTIONARY/PREPAREDNESS ACTIONS...
* Prepare, plan and stay informed. Visit http://go.usa.gov/c7kkP</description>
